<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: NES Game Project #1]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=10207&amp;p=116418#p116418"><![CDATA[
It's with a little disappointment that I have to announce that this project has been put on hiatus.  Mike and I agreed to cease working on it together for the time being, due to differences in priorities and ability to contribute (basically I became the only one making progress while he was tied up with full-time work.  i am a freelancer.)<br /><br />But!  All is not in vain.  I decided to show off the small concrete progress we made up to this point.  Since I expect what I create from here on to be more in my own direction.  I figure no sense in keeping the old stuff to myself now.  In the span of the past few weeks I created these graphics and got them displaying on the NES.  I also got the player's character running around with the crosspad.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=6048">sonder</a> — Mon Aug 12, 2013 12:53 pm</p><hr />
